Block
if statement expects only one statement in its body.
要在if's or else's statement body中新增語句，要使用大括號也稱作braces {}
it's good practice always to use braces {}
braces {} 括號中的語句（如control statement's or function's body)形成一個block
block 可以放置single statement 的 function 任何地方

if (studentGrade >= 60) {
   cout << "Passed";
}
else {
   cout << "Failed\n";
   cout << "You must retake this course";
}


block可以用於限定變數的作用域、分組語句、控制程式流程等。